Interface UISecurityConstraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActorBasedSecurityConstraint, CustomSecurityConstraint, DeclarativeUIConstraint, RoleBasedSecurityConstraint, UCBasedSecurityConstraint

    public interface UISecurityConstraint
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'UI Security Constraint'. Superclasse di tutti i security constraints applicabili a widget e menu.

    The following features are supported:

    • Visible
    • Enabled
